<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Elevana Registration Confirmation</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lexend:wght@100..900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Lexend", sans-serif;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .email-header {
      background-color: #f4f7f2;
      color: black;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 8px 5px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .email-header span {
      color: #66A23B;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 10px 5px;
    }

    .name {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .password-box {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }

    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f4f7f2;
      padding: 15px 5px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to <span>Elevana</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p class="name">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for registering with Elevana!</p>
      <p>Your account has been successfully created. Here is your temporary password:</p>
      <div class="password-box"><%= password %></div>
      <p>You can log in using this password and change it anytime from your profile settings for better security.</p>
      <p>If you did not sign up for an Elevana account, please ignore this message.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at <a href="#">support@elevana.com</a></p>
      <p>&copy; 2025 Elevana. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
